- Update to 1.2.6:
  - Performance improvements to group mirroring (from
    `Denver Janke <https://bitbucket.org/denverjanke>`_).
  - Add :data:`django_auth_ldap.backend.ldap_error` signal for custom handling of
    :exc:`~ldap.LDAPError` exceptions.
